 &lt;h2>Why CNN Came into Existence?&lt;/h2>

 &lt;p>
 CNNs were introduced out of necessity. &lt;strong>Traditional neural networks (ANNs)&lt;/strong> struggled when faced with
 image data.&lt;br />
 They treated images as a flat list of numbers, which made it hard to identify &lt;strong>patterns, textures, and
 spatial relationships&lt;/strong>.
